OL,3,CSNP and Greens have final chance to
OL,4,Cback Murrell probe, says Labour
OL,6,FWednesday will be the "final chance"
OL,7,Ffor the SNP and Greens to "do the
OL,8,Fright thing" and back a parliamentary
OL,9,Finquiry into Peter Murrell, Labour has
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,FThe party has tabled a motion which
OL,13,Fwill be put before MSPs on Wednesday
OL,14,Fafternoon, ordering a Holyrood probe
OL,15,Finto the former SNP chief executive's
OL,16,Fembezzlement of more than #400,000
OL,17,Fspent on scores of personal items.
OL,26,@nD@WOUnD@dO]oD@[OUpD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
