OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781053389
OL,3,CSNP and Greens have final chance to
OL,4,Cback Murrell probe, says Labour
OL,6,FBut the SNP has been resistant to
OL,7,Fcalls, with First Minister John
OL,8,FSwinney saying there "can be no higher
OL,9,Finvestigation" than the police probe,
OL,10,Fdubbed Operation Branchform, which
OL,11,Fsnared Murrell.
OL,13,FBut ahead of the vote, Labour deputy
OL,14,Fleader Jackie Baillie said: "It is
OL,15,Fwithout doubt that there are still
OL,16,Fsignificant and serious questions to
OL,17,Fbe answered about Peter Murrell's
OL,18,Fcriminal activity and the SNP culture
OL,19,Fthat enabled it to happen.
OL,26,@pD@VOUqD@NO]vD@]OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781053389
OL,3,CSNP and Greens have final chance to
OL,4,Cback Murrell probe, says Labour
OL,6,F"For years, those at the top of the
OL,7,FSNP have sought to shut down and
OL,8,Fsilence whistleblowers and cover up
OL,9,Fany wrongdoing.
OL,11,F"That has utterly eroded the public's
OL,12,Ftrust in Scottish politics and the
OL,13,Fgoverning party.
OL,15,F"It is right that lessons are learned
OL,16,Ffrom Operation Branchform and this
OL,17,Fterrible scandal so that we can give
OL,18,Fthe public the reassurances they need,
OL,19,Fparticularly when it comes to how
OL,20,Ftheir money is handled."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUwD@AOU|D@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
