OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781053389
OL,3,CSNP and Greens have final chance to
OL,4,Cback Murrell probe, says Labour
OL,6,FMs Baillie went on to appeal to SNP
OL,7,Fand Green MSPs to back the party's
OL,8,Fattempts to set up the inquiry.
OL,10,F"We know that John Swinney and others
OL,11,Fwithin the SNP, along with Ross Greer,
OL,12,Fhave had close friendships with
OL,13,FMurrell, openly praising him for his
OL,14,Fstewardship of the SNP as chief
OL,15,Fexecutive," she said.
OL,17,F"However, they must set aside their
OL,18,Fpersonal connections with Murrell and
OL,19,Frealise that it is only right that we
OL,20,Fnow have an inquiry into this scandal
OL,21,Fto allow Scotland to move forward.
OL,26,@rD@AOUwD@KO]yD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781053389
OL,3,CSNP and Greens have final chance to
OL,4,Cback Murrell probe, says Labour
OL,6,F"They have so far dug their heels in
OL,7,Fon the issue of an inquiry, but they
OL,8,Fstill have a final chance to do the
OL,9,Fright thing, back the motion and allow
OL,10,Fthe Scottish Parliament to hold an
OL,11,Finquiry."
OL,13,FA spokesman for the SNP said: "Jackie
OL,14,FBaillie just chaired the Labour
OL,15,Fcampaign which led them to their worst
OL,16,Fresult in history, and it is not
OL,17,Fdifficult to see why.
OL,19,F"Rather than focusing on the
OL,20,Fpriorities of the people of Scotland,
OL,21,FLabour are focused on smears like this.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@IO]uD@_OU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
