OL,3,CSNP and Greens have final chance to
OL,4,Cback Murrell probe, says Labour
OL,6,FThe Scottish Government has also
OL,7,Ftabled an amendment to the motion,
OL,8,Fwhich claims the probe would be a
OL,9,F"conflict of interest" due to MSPs
OL,10,Flooking into the affairs of "rival
OL,11,Fpolitical parties" and urges "elected
OL,12,Frepresentatives to use their
OL,13,Fparliamentary time to address matters
OL,14,Fthat will improve the lives of the
OL,15,Fpeople of Scotland including, tackling
OL,16,Fthe cost-of-living crisis, improving
OL,17,Fpublic services such as this NHS and
OL,18,Ftaking climate action".
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@VO]rD@]OUsD@RO]sD@^OUzD@VO]
