OL,3,CSNP and Greens have final chance to
OL,4,Cback Murrell probe, says Labour
OL,6,FA Green amendment will also call for
OL,7,Fan independent review of political
OL,8,Fparty finances in a bid to avoid a
OL,9,F"nakedly partisan process".
OL,11,FThe Scottish Greens have been
OL,12,Fcontacted for comment.
